---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import BottomNav from '../components/BottomNav.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - Mershal" description="Mershal Terms of Service - Rules and guidelines for using our website">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 pb-20 md:pb-8 font-sans text-slate-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-black text-slate-950 mb-3">Terms of Service</h1>
      
      <div class="bg-slate-100 border-l-4 border-primary-crimson p-4 rounded-r-lg mb-8 shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
          <strong>Last updated:</strong> June 1, 2026
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-6">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing and using Mershal (mershal.in, "the website"), you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provisions of this agreement.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-6">2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p>Mershal is a digital publication providing:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>AI Tool guides and software workflows</li>
          <li>SaaS reviews, metrics, and comparisons</li>
          <li>Productivity app reviews and framework guides</li>
          <li>Freelancing, online business, and digital marketing insights</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-6">3. User Conduct</h2>
        <p>You agree not to use the website to post unlawful, offensive, or harmful content, attempt to bypass access controls, or gather user data without authorization.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-6">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All design assets, layout systems, original articles, logos, and scripts are the property of Mershal. Reproducing, re-publishing, or scraping our content without express consent is strictly prohibited.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-6">5. Disclaimers & Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>The content provided on Mershal is for educational and informational purposes only. We make no guarantees regarding accuracy, software updates, pricing fluctuations, or availability. Mershal is not liable for operational failures resulting from decisions made using our reviews.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-6">6. Third-Party Links & Advertising</h2>
        <p>We feature third-party advertisements via Google AdSense and incorporate affiliate or sponsor referral links. We are not responsible for policies or content displayed on external destination sites.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-6">7. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of India.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-6">8. Contact Information</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about these terms, please contact us at:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Email: <a href="mailto:legal@mershal.in" class="text-primary-crimson hover:underline font-bold">legal@mershal.in</a></li>
          <li>Address: Kolkata, West Bengal, India</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
  <BottomNav />
</Layout>